import React from "react";
import './index.css'
import Logo from '../elements/logo/Logo.js';

const Navbox = () => (
   
    <svg width={226} height={1080} viewBox="0 0 226 1080" className="navbox">
     <Logo />
    <defs>
      <style>
        {
          ".a{fill:#fff;stroke:#edf5f5;}.b{stroke:none;}.c{fill:none;}.d{filter:url(#a);}"
        }
      </style>
      <filter
        id="a"
        x={0}
        y={0}
        width={226}
        height={1080}
        filterUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
      >
        <feOffset dy={3} input="SourceAlpha" />
        <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation={3} result="b" />
        <feFlood floodOpacity={0.161} />
        <feComposite operator="in" in2="b" />
        <feComposite in="SourceGraphic" />
      </filter>
    </defs>
    <g transform="translate(9 6)">
      <g className="d" transform="matrix(1, 0, 0, 1, -9, -6)">
        <g className="a" transform="translate(9 6)">
          <path
            className="b"
            d="M0,0H158a50,50,0,0,1,50,50V1062a0,0,0,0,1,0,0H0a0,0,0,0,1,0,0V0A0,0,0,0,1,0,0Z"
          />
          <path
            className="c"
            d="M1,.5H158A49.5,49.5,0,0,1,207.5,50V1061a.5.5,0,0,1-.5.5H1a.5.5,0,0,1-.5-.5V1A.5.5,0,0,1,1,.5Z"
          />
        </g>
      </g>
    </g>
  </svg>
);

export default Navbox;
